  "title": "Digital Marketing Manager (International)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Duties: </strong></p><ul><li>Create and run digital marketing plans.</li><li>Manage our global social media accounts (Instagram, LinkedIn, Facebook, X).</li><li>Write and share content that engages international shipping and logistics clients.</li><li>Run online campaigns to generate leads and attract customers.</li><li>Track results and report on what's working to HQ.</li><li>Work with sales and operations teams to support business goals.</li><li>Help tell the story of our innovative technology, like our work in AI.</li></ul><p><strong>What You Need</strong></p><ul><li><p>Bachelor's degree in Marketing, Business, or a related field.</p></li><li><p>5+ years of digital marketing experience (B2B or logistics is a plus).</p></li><li><p>Hands-on skill with social media and digital ads.</p></li><li><p>Excellent communication skills.</p></li><li><p>Ability to create good content and analyze campaign data.</p></li><li><p>Self-starter who can work independently with a team in China.</p></li></ul><p><strong>KPI</strong></p><ul><li><p>Growing our international social media followers and engagement.</p></li><li><p>More people knowing our brand in target countries.</p></li><li><p>Getting quality leads from your campaigns.</p></li><li><p>Providing clear and useful reports to HQ.</p></li></ul>",
